  "lastUpdatedOn": "2013-03-01",
  "religion": "Perry is non-religious, though he has some Jewish heritage.",
  "politicalViews": "Perry is a liberal Democrat.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Mathew Perry was born in Williamstown, Massachusetts and grew up in Ottawa, Ontario, Canada."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Rumors abound that Perry is part Jewish.",
      "sourceTitle": "The Ethnic Backgrounds of the Cast of Friends and Seinfeld (Yes, Most of Them are Jewish; Even Matthew Perry)",
      "sourceUrl": "http://nickshell1983.wordpress.com/2010/05/26/the-ethnic-backgrounds-of-the-cast-of-friends-and-seinfeld/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " But that may not be the case as his parents were married in a Catholic ceremony.",
      "sourceTitle": "Ottawa Citizen – Google News Archive Search",
      "sourceUrl": "http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=lboyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5ewFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4626,2377310&dq=john-bennett-perry&hl=en."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Perry does not come off as religious. The closest he's come to religion seems to have been during his struggles with addiction. At some point, while shooting for his now-defunct TV show, "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "Serving Sara"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "text": ", he had a moment of clarity. He said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5,
      "parentId": 4
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[I had] this very lovely spiritual moment… Everything's clear for one split second. I realize, I've got to go save myself. I got on the phone and called the people who were willing to help me.",
      "sourceTitle": "The Fame He Craved Came, But It Wasn't Enough",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.nytimes.com/2002/08/18/arts/film-the-fame-he-craved-came-but-it-wasn-t-enough.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "However, he's been known to take cracks at religious people and their faith. For example, he made a parody video making fun of Angus T. Jones' "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "link",
      "text": "video",
      "sourceUrl": "http://tvline.com/2012/11/26/angus-t-jones-two-and-a-half-men-controversy/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " in which he implored viewers to not watch his \"immoral\" show "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "2 and a Half Men"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " for religious reasons. Perry says:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8,
      "parentId": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I decided to sit down for an hour and skim the entire Bible… crazy stuff… glancing at the Bible has led me to realize that my show, "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "Go On"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": ", is a complete abomination with terrible morals. Don't watch my show… Because I think all of my TV shows were immoral, I'm gonna give all the money back. I assume that's what Angus is going to do.",
      "sourceTitle": "Matthew Perry's Testimony (Pt.2)",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.funnyordie.com/videos/71b785e64e/matthew-perry-s-testimony-pt-2"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 9,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "So, it's mostly a big joke for Perry. We're going with the non-religious tag.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 10
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Witty, sarcastic politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Perry isn't all that political either. However, it's pretty easy to see which side of the fence he sits on. He's gone on Bill Maher's "
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "Real Time with Bill Maher"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " to talk about his negative opinion of the outrageous conservatism rampant in Fox News.",
      "sourceTitle": "Matthew Perry – Bill Maher – Brett Baier",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.mediaite.com/tv/matthew-perry-calls-foxs-bret-baier-a-scared-asshole-on-bill-maher-panel/"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "And though he never endorsed Obama, during election day 2012, Perry tweeted:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 14,
      "parentId": 13
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Now that's what I call a speech. #GoBama",
      "sourceTitle": "matthew perry (MatthewPerry) on Twitter.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://twitter.com/MatthewPerry"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 15
    },
    {
      "parentId": 15,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "And after the Sandy Hook shooting, Perry started retweeting gun control tweets and when a longtime fan misinterpreted one and asked him if he was pro-gun, he replied:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 17,
      "parentId": 16
    },
    {
      "parentId": 17,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "No, twit, I was saying quite the opposite.",
      "sourceTitle": "matthew perry (MatthewPerry) on Twitter.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://twitter.com/MatthewPerry"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 18
    },
    {
      "parentId": 18,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "So, we've got ourselves another Hollywood liberal Democrat–not that there's anything wrong with that."
    }
  ],
